==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Calisthenics
<hw>Cal`is*then"ics</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The science,
art, or practice of healthful exercise of the body and limbs, to promote
strength, gracefulness, and general fitness; light gymnastics.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> calisthenics, calisthenic exercise, callisthenic
exercise.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Caliver</ent>⟦br⟧
